CHAN SHEE, alias Chan Suey Gin, v. John D. NAGLE, Commissioner of Immigration of the Port of San Francisco. No. 6710. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 18, 1932. Joseph P. Fallon, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Geo. J. Hatfield, U. S. Atty., of San Francisco, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellant, ordered appeal dismissed.
